      "date": "2014-09-04 17:53:08.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nPlease consider updating the commit message to correct some grammar mistakes:\n\nLU-5380 at: reset AT after connect\n\nOnce connected, any previously gathered AT statistics may no longer be\nvalid because they may reflect other routing, etc. The connect by itself\ncould take a long time for different reasons (e.g. the server was not\nready) and net latency got very high (see import_select_connection())\nwhich may not reflect the current situation.\n\nTake into account only the current (re-)CONNECT rpc latency.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
